{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870511803,"sessionID":"ses_285dead53ffenYhgGCpNqgy0g0","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2185be001hXpBSG2J6mPmY3","messageID":"msg_d7a217d8d001cs5bg65oSosk3T","sessionID":"ses_285dead53ffenYhgGCpNqgy0g0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_324a008e22ba4559a05064b4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** sdk-python  \n4: **Language:** Python  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Stage:** ST-1 (Spec Drafting)\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Implementation Tasks\n11: \n12: *(Tasks to be defined after spec is finalized)*\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Dependencies\n17: \n18: | Task | Depends On |\n19: |------|------------|\n20: | T001 | - |\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## Verification Checklist\n25: \n26: *(Acceptance criteria to be defined after spec is finalized)*\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## References\n31: \n32: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md`\n33: - Design: `python-sdk/design.md`\n34: - Spec: `python-sdk/spec.md`\n35: - Related: AR-028 (AgentRuntimeClient implementation)\n\n(End of file - total 35 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 Tasks\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Spec Drafting)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n*(Tasks to be defined after spec is finalized)*\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T001 | - |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775870511782,"end":1775870511801}}}}
