n_header`\n\n- [ ] **T015** Test x-agentcube-session-id header in AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n  - *File:* `tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Header present in requests\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::test_session_header`\n\n- [ ] **T016** Test timeout tuple construction\n  - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* timeout=(connect_timeout, self.timeout)\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_timeout_tuple`\n\n- [ ] **T017** Test per-call timeout override (timeout + 2.0)\n  - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* execute_command(timeout=60) uses 62s read timeout\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_per_call_timeout`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests - URL & Body (T018-T022)\n\n- [ ] **T018** Test ControlPlaneClient base_url from env var\n  - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env var used\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_base_url_from_env`\n\n- [ ] **T019** Test ControlPlaneClient base_url from argument\n  - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Argument takes precedence over env var\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_base_url_from_arg`\n\n- [ ] **T020** Test CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient URL construction\n  - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* URL format: `/v1/namespaces/{ns}/code-interpreters/{cr}/invocations/`\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_url_construction`\n\n- [ ] **T021** Test execute_command request body format\n  - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"60s\"}`\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_execute_command_body`\n\n- [ ] **T022** Test write_file base64 encoding\n  - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n  - *Verify:* Content is base64 encoded in body\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_write_file_encoding`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: Unit Tests - Token & Logging (T023-T027)\n\n- [ ] **T023** Test read_token_from_file with existing file\n  - *File:* `tests/test_utils.py`\n  - *Verify:* Returns token string (stripped)\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_utils.py::test_read_token_from_file_exists`\n\n- [ ] **T024** Test read_token_from_file with missing file\n  - *File:* `tests/test_utils.py`\n  - *Verify:* Returns None, no exception\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_utils.py::test_read_token_from_file_missing`\n\n- [ ] **T025** Test get_logger default level (INFO)\n  - *File:* `tests/test_log.py`\n  - *Verify:* Logger level is INFO\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_log.py::test_logger_default_level`\n\n- [ ] **T026** Test get_logger with verbose=True (DEBUG)\n  - *File:* `tests/test_log.py`\n  - *Verify:* Logger level is DEBUG\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_log.py::test_logger_verbose`\n\n- [ ] **T027** Test exception hierarchy\n  - *File:* `tests/test_exceptions.py`\n  - *Verify:* All exceptions inherit from AgentCubeError\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_exceptions.py::test_exception_hierarchy`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 6: Integration & Lint (T028-T030)\n\n- [ ] **T028** Run all AR-029 unit tests\n  - *Verify:* All pytest tests pass\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/ -v --tb=short 2>&1 | grep -E \"(PASSED|FAILED|ERROR)\"`\n\n- [ ] **T029** Test ControlPlaneClient with mock server\n  - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane_integration.py`\n  - *Verify:* create_session and delete_session work with mock HTTP\n  - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane_integration.py`\n\n- [ ] **T030** Run linter/typecheck on all modified files\n  - *Verify:* ruff and mypy pass\n  - *Test:* `ruff check agentcube/ && mypy agentcube/`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T002 | T001 |\n| T004 | T003 |\n| T006 | T005 |\n| T008 | T007 |\n| T009 | T001, 